metadata.description:
This is a living collection to celebrate trans people. 

Each minted nft is a portion from the second artwork that I created with Ai:

https://ipfs.io/ipfs/QmYyFRKVo3Fsk9HhxfYKJ2FFYkorfAtBrv25Ka5L59F3KK/nft.jpg

My intention is to continually add to this original artwork, mint those additions here as they are made.

100% of the revenue from this collection, for all time, will be donated to transgender related charities. 

I kicked it off with a $2,000 donation to The Trevor Project. (Donation Date 02/19/2023 - Donation Number: 78496926)
